ad, this could be a sign that you are a victim of medical fraud. [1]\";s:4:\"type\";s:5:\"image\";}i:876;a:7:{s:6:\"status\";s:6:\"active\";s:3:\"src\";s:112:\"https://toolsandtips.metlifedefender.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/27-Image-Carousel-Medical-Fraud-Slide-61.jpg\";s:5:\"title\";s:51:\"27 – Image Carousel – Medical Fraud – Slide 6\";s:4:\"link\";s:0:\"\";s:3:\"alt\";s:51:\"27 – Image Carousel – Medical Fraud – Slide 6\";s:7:\"caption\";s:323:\"<strong>Your Wallet:</strong> Between credit cards, loyalty rewards, and your driver’s license, your Social Security card may seem like just another item to stash in the wallet and go. It’s important, however to make sure your sensitive information is stored in a safe, secure location that only you have access to. [1]\";s:4:\"type\";s:5:\"image\";}i:1012;a:7:{s:6:\"status\";s:6:\"active\";s:3:\"src\";s:110:\"https://toolsandtips.metlifedefender.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/MetLife-Defender-Logo-Image-Galleries2.jpg\";s:5:\"title\";s:39:\"MetLife-Defender-Logo—Image-Galleries\";s:4:\"link\";s:0:\"\";s:3:\"alt\";s:39:\"MetLife-Defender-Logo—Image-Galleries\";s:7:\"caption\";s:298:\"Protect your medical identity no matter the location: MetLife Defender can help protect you by tracking your data and safeguarding your personal information. \n\n<a href=\"https://toolsandtips.metlifedefender.com/medical-fraud-protection/\">Click here</a> to find out more about medical identity fraud.\";s:4:\"type\";s:5:\"image\";}}s:2:\"id\";i:872;s:6:\"config\";a:12:{s:4:\"type\";s:7:\"default\";s:12:\"slider_theme\";s:4:\"base\";s:12:\"slider_width\";i:800;s:13:\"slider_height\";i:450;s:10:\"transition\";s:4:\"fade\";s:8:\"duration\";i:5000;s:5:\"speed\";i:400;s:6:\"gutter\";i:20;s:6:\"slider\";i:1;s:7:\"classes\";a:1:{i:0;s:0:\"\";}s:5:\"title\";s:41:\"5 Places Your Medical Records Are at Risk\";s:4:\"slug\";s:41:\"5-places-your-medical-records-are-at-risk\";}}i:3;a:3:{s:2:\"id\";i:853;s:6:\"slider\";a:8:{i:854;a:7:{s:6:\"status\";s:6:\